    "Q1: Scan 60M lineitem with early filter on l_shipdate (99% pass). Pre-size hash table for 6 groups. Parallel 64-core execution with morsel-driven approach. Use SIMD for discount/price calculations. Zone map on l_shipdate for block pruning.",
